Change log for Lingua::Identify::CLD2

0.02
  - Changed API to accept hash of options as second parameter.
  - Fixed return value.
  - Fixed LanguageCloseSet to accept string language codes (in addition to integer numbers).
  - Croak on invalid UTF-8.

0.01  Mon Jun 08 10:41:00 2015
  - Initial release to CPAN.

